Set Height 750
Source "recordings/tapes/shared-config.tape"
Output "recordings/svgs/tools/list-query-send-email.svg"
Output "recordings/ascii/tools/list-query-send-email.ascii"

Hide
Type "# List with --query filter"
Enter
Show
Type "composio tools list --query 'send email'"
Sleep 300ms
Enter
Sleep 6s
